{"tid":2200880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"家屬怒斥華春瑩「生安白造」 朱凱廸料中共利用12人上演「港獨大戲」","createTime":"2020-09-13T10:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T13:15:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":45,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5c49d1bbc2b2fed64408fdbbe55424d6982cf945","tid":2200880,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"12名港青上月23日疑偷渡往台灣途中，被廣東海警拘捕至今，音訊全無，未知安危。中國外交部發言人華春瑩未審先判，直指12名港人企圖把香港從中國分裂出去。<br />\n<br />\n有份協助12名被捕港人家屬的本土派人士鄒家成引述兩名被捕者家屬，批評華春瑩的言論「生安白造」，亦可見事態已經相當嚴重。鄒認為華春瑩將事件升級至分裂國家層面，反映被扣留港人的處境將更危險；同樣向家屬提供協助的朱凱廸則指，可以預視中共會利用此12人上演「港獨大戲」，不排除往後有「電視認罪」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YBBHIDK5LZFE7ASTYYHG3HC4KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYBBHIDK5LZFE7ASTYYHG3HC4KU%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a43b6292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FYBBHIDK5LZFE7ASTYYHG3HC4KU%2F&h=7798780a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/YBBHIDK5LZFE7ASTYYHG3HC4KU/</a>"},{"pid":"0fc3f1cfb68ab915a4a9d520c57332fa843c66cb","tid":2200880,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b403a5fc689cea9ba01ff0c1235b615b4260f53","tid":2200880,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img